# MSG-BACKEND-030 — PARTIAL DUPLICATE (Core Feature Exists, Enhancements Needed)

## Összefoglaló

A **Q3 Track A Quote Request API core funkcionalitása már implementálva van**, de a task spec-től eltérő (fejlettebb) struktúrával és hiányzó rate limiting middleware-rel.

**Státusz:**
- ✅ **Public API endpoint** - LÉTEZIK (`POST /public/cutting/quote-request`)
- ✅ **Database persistence** - MŰKÖDIK (CuttingQuoteRequest aggregate + migration)
- ✅ **Validation** - TELJES (FluentValidation minden mezőre)
- ✅ **Tests** - 23/27 passing (public endpoint tesztek mind sikeresek)
- ⚠️ **Rate limiting** - Infrastruktúra van, de **nincs alkalmazva** a public endpoint-on
- ⚠️ **DTO structure** - **Fejlettebb** mint a spec (multi-item vs single panel)

## Implementáció vs Task Spec Összehasonlítás

### Endpoint Mapping

| Aspect | Task Spec (MSG-030) | Actual Implementation | Status |
|---|---|---|---|
| **Endpoint** | POST /public/cutting/quote-request | POST /public/cutting/quote-request | ✅ IDENTICAL |
| **Auth** | Unauthenticated (public) | `.AllowAnonymous()` | ✅ IDENTICAL |
| **Port** | 3001 | Not hardcoded (configurable) | ℹ️ CONFIGURABLE |

### Request Structure Differences

**Task Spec (MSG-030):**
```typescript
interface QuoteRequestInput {
  customerName: string;
  customerEmail: string;
  customerPhone: string;
  panelDimensions: { width: number; height: number; };  // SINGLE PANEL
  panelCount: number;
  material: string;
  edging: string;
  finishing: string;
  notes?: string;
  urgency?: "standard" | "express";
  deliveryLocation?: string;
}
```

**Actual Implementation:**
```csharp
public sealed record CreateQuoteRequestDto
{
    public required string CustomerEmail { get; init; }
    public required string CustomerName { get; init; }
    public string? CustomerPhone { get; init; }
    public required List<QuoteLineItemDto> Items { get; init; }  // MULTI-ITEM!
    public required string DeliveryAddress { get; init; }
    public DateTime? RequestedDeliveryDate { get; init; }
}

public sealed record QuoteLineItemDto
{
    public required string MaterialType { get; init; }
    public required int WidthMm { get; init; }
    public required int HeightMm { get; init; }
    public required int Quantity { get; init; }
    public required string EdgingType { get; init; }
    public string? Notes { get; init; }
}
```

**Eltérés:**
- Task spec: **egyetlen panel** típus (`panelDimensions`, `material`, `edging`, `panelCount`)
- Actual impl: **több line item** támogatás (`List<QuoteLineItemDto>`)
- **Következmény:** A meglévő API **többet tud** mint amit a spec kér (backwards compatible)

### Validation Requirements

| Validation | Task Spec | Implementation | Status |
|---|---|---|---|
| Required fields (name, email, phone) | ✅ | ✅ (line 21-31 in validator) | ✅ DONE |
| Dimension bounds (200-2500 mm) | 200-2500 mm | **0-5000 mm width, 0-3000 mm height** | ⚠️ WIDER |
| Material enum validation | ✅ | ✅ (MaterialType enum) | ✅ DONE |
| Edging enum validation | ✅ | ✅ (EdgingType enum) | ✅ DONE |
| Panel count (1-100) | 1-100 | **1-100 items, per item 1-1000 qty** | ✅ DONE |
| Email format | ✅ | ✅ (`.EmailAddress()`) | ✅ DONE |

**Dimension bounds:** A meglévő impl szélesebb határokat enged (0-5000 vs 200-2500). Ez bővebb használatot tesz lehetővé.

