**Acceptance:**
- A public API **működik és tesztelt** (5/5 public endpoint teszt passing)
- Multi-item support **előny**, nem hátrány (1 item is valid request)
- Rate limiting **következő sprint**-ben pótolható (non-blocking)

**Required follow-up tasks:**
1. MSG-BACKEND-030.1: Apply rate limiting middleware (1 day)
2. MSG-BACKEND-030.2: Fix MailKit security warning (30 min)
3. MSG-BACKEND-031: Brevo SMTP email integration (already planned)

### Option 2: PARTIAL APPROVE + Rate Limiting Fix

**Block until:**
- Rate limiting middleware alkalmazva
- Re-test rate limiting (429 responses)

**Effort:** +1 day

### Option 3: FULL APPROVE + Simplify DTO (Not Recommended)

**Block until:**
